hopobject.body: Have you read any good books lately? horowitzpharmacy.com In bankruptcy, Kodak failed to obtain significant value forits portfolio of patents, which experts said was a crucialreason it had to sell core businesses and reinvent itself. Butthe bankruptcy resolved a major dispute with retirees overpensions, and it has forged a restructuring plan that, whilewiping out shareholders, should pay secured creditors andsecond-lien noteholders in full.
